1. Press the Start Game button to start the game.

2. Once you reach the save slot screen, you can create a new character by specifying a name, and you
 will be prompted to select your customizations. After that, you can press start game to start
 playing the game.

3. When multiple save slots are populated, you can click on them and the information associated
with them will be displayed on the screen.

4. You can double click on any saved slot to reconfigure preferences, or delete the slot.